data.description:
Open House Saturday August 23rd 1:00-3:00pm

PRICED TO SELL!! Motivated seller!! Bring us your BEST offer and let's make something work!! Seller can close in 3 WEEKS OR LESS!!!

New Granite Countertops! Location, Location, Location! This area can't be beat!! This is a must see 3 level townhome! 4 bedrooms! 3 bathrooms! 2 car garage! Cozy Stone Fireplace! 100% finished basement! End unit in a small complex! Family-Friendly neighborhood! Mountain Views! All appliances included! Fully fenced extra LARGE yard! Close to grocery, restaurants, shopping, freeway and easy access to ski resorts up Big & Little Cottonwood Canyons!
